    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p>\n<p>Prerequisite: Hozuki Clan, Level 12+</p>\n<p>You adapted more to using Water jutsu, making yourself better at manipulating your own Water. <br />You gain the following Benefits:</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>• Increase your Strength or Constitution score by 1, to a maximum of 20. </p>\n<p><br />• Ninjutsu, you cast with the Water Release keyword and no other nature release keyword, can use your Constitution as your Ninjutsu ability modifier. </p>\n<p><br />• Your other Hijutsu gain the benefits of you Hydrofication even when you are not concentrating on it</p>",
